inputs/bustle.txt:The morning after death
inputs/bustle.txt:The sweeping up the heart,
inputs/fox.txt:The quick brown fox jumps over the lazy dog.
inputs/nobody.txt:Then there's a pair of us!
inputs/nobody.txt:Don't tell! they'd advertise—you know!
inputs/nobody.txt:To tell one's name—the livelong June—
